{
  "texts": [
    "Genetic distances were calculated using the Kosambi mapping function, and the map was created using MapChart (v2.32) 91.",
    "Markers flanking LR39 were anchored to the TA1675 reference assembly.",
    "Annotated high-confidence genes at the delimited physical interval were screened for protein homology using BLASTp to identify diversity between TA1675 and AL8/78 (Supplementary Table 13).",
    "The conserved domains and critical residues of WTK and NLR were identified using the amino acid sequences in the NCBI Conserved Domain search (https://www.ncbi.",
    "nlm.nih.gov/Structure/cdd/wrpsb.cgi) and InterPro (https://www."
